{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877660875,"sessionID":"ses_285719541ffesa1zcm3d36gX9c","part":{"id":"prt_d7a8e9b2b001zbrGoXxFBm9khi","messageID":"msg_d7a8e9034001ZhXP2uwsjB2YEp","sessionID":"ses_285719541ffesa1zcm3d36gX9c","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_c1fa673b60b84be59565f3d7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-034/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-034/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Design: AR-034 вҖ” CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: [TODO: High-level design overview]\n6: \n7: ## Architecture\n8: \n9: ### Workflow Directory Structure\n10: \n11: ```\n12: .github/\n13: в””в”Җв”Җ workflows/\n14:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ ci/\n15:     в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ build.yml\n16:     в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ test.yml\n17:     в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ lint.yml\n18:     в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ security.yml\n19:     в”ңв”Җв”Җ cd/\n20:     в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ deploy-staging.yml\n21:     в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ deploy-production.yml\n22:     в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ publish.yml\n23:     в””в”Җв”Җ utils/\n24:         в”ңв”Җв”Җ triage.yml\n25:         в”ңв”Җв”Җ update-changelog.yml\n26:         в””в”Җв”Җ sync.yml\n27: ```\n28: \n29: ### Workflow Design Patterns\n30: \n31: #### Common Patterns\n32: \n33: - **Trigger patterns**: Event-based (push, PR, schedule, manual)\n34: - **Job orchestration**: Sequential vs parallel execution\n35: - **Artifact management**: Build artifacts, test reports\n36: - **Secret management**: GitHub Secrets integration\n37: - **Matrix strategies**: Multi-version/multi-platform testing\n38: \n39: #### Shared Configuration\n40: \n41: [TODO: Define reusable workflows and composite actions]\n42: \n43: ## Implementation Details\n44: \n45: ### Workflow 1: TBD\n46: \n47: ```yaml\n48: # TBD\n49: ```\n50: \n51: ---\n52: \n53: ## Security Considerations\n54: \n55: - Secret rotation strategy\n56: - Permission least privilege\n57: - OIDC token usage\n58: - Environment protection rules\n59: \n60: ---\n61: \n62: ## Performance Optimization\n63: \n64: - Caching strategies\n65: - Parallel job execution\n66: - Skipping redundant runs\n67: \n68: ---\n69: \n70: ## Monitoring & Observability\n71: \n72: - Workflow run metrics\n73: - Failure alerting\n74: - Duration tracking\n75: \n76: (End of file)\n\n(End of file - total 76 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Design: AR-034 вҖ” CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n\n## Overview\n\n[TODO: High-level design overview]\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Workflow Directory Structure\n\n```\n.github/\nв””в”Җв”Җ workflows/\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ ci/\n    в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ build.yml\n    в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ test.yml\n    в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ lint.yml\n    в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ security.yml\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ cd/\n    в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ deploy-staging.yml","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-034/design.md","time":{"start":1775877660856,"end":1775877660873}}}}
