{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877728467,"sessionID":"ses_285719541ffesa1zcm3d36gX9c","part":{"id":"prt_d7a8efb5a001QOtT7zMJreF817","messageID":"msg_d7a8ef0a1001rhcycFP3XQwdf6","sessionID":"ses_285719541ffesa1zcm3d36gX9c","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_43f41ec7fcc44108a46b7926","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Design: AR-035 вҖ” client-go зұ»еһӢе®ўжҲ·з«Ҝз”ҹжҲҗ\n\n## Overview\n\nз”ҹжҲҗ Kubernetes client д»Јз ҒпјҢз”ЁдәҺ API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh / v1alpha1`пјҢжЁЎеқ—и·Ҝеҫ„ `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`гҖӮиҜҘе®ўжҲ·з«Ҝеә“йҒөеҫӘ Kubernetes client-go и§„иҢғпјҢжҸҗдҫӣ typed clientгҖҒinformerгҖҒlister е®Ңж•ҙз”ҹжҖҒгҖӮ\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Directory Structure\n\n```\nclient-go/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ clientset/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ versioned/\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ clientset.go              # Clientset дё»е…ҘеҸЈ\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ scheme/                   # зұ»еһӢжіЁеҶҢ\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ register.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ doc.go\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ typed/\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ runtime/\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ v1alpha1/\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ           в”ңв”Җв”Җ runtime_client.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ           в”ңв”Җв”Җ agentruntime.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ           в”ңв”Җв”Җ codeinterpreter.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ           в”ңв”Җв”Җ generated_expansion.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ           в”ңв”Җв”Җ doc.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ           в””в”Җв”Җ fake/\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ               в”ңв”Җв”Җ fake_runtime_client.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ               в”ңв”Җв”Җ fake_agentruntime.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ               в”ңв”Җв”Җ fake_codeinterpreter.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ               в””в”Җв”Җ doc.go\nв”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ fake/\nв”Ӯ           в”ңв”Җв”Җ clientset_generated.go\nв”Ӯ           в”ңв”Җв”Җ register.go\nв”Ӯ           в””в”Җв”Җ doc.go\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ informers/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ externalversions/\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ factory.go                 # SharedInformerFactory\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ generic.go                 # GenericInformer и·Ҝз”ұ\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ runtime/\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ interface.go           # Group жҺҘеҸЈ\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ v1alpha1/\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ interface.go       # Version жҺҘеҸЈ\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ agentruntime.go\nв”Ӯ       в”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ codeinterpreter.go\nв”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ internalinterfaces/\nв”Ӯ           в””в”Җв”Җ factory_interfaces.go\nв””в”Җв”Җ listers/\n    в””в”Җв”Җ runtime/\n        в””в”Җв”Җ v1alpha1/\n            в”ңв”Җв”Җ agentruntime.go\n            в”ңв”Җв”Җ codeinterpreter.go\n            в””в”Җв”Җ expansion_generated.go\n```\n\n### Component Responsibilities\n\n| Component | Responsibility |\n|-----------|----------------|\n| Clientset | йЎ¶еұӮе…ҘеҸЈпјҢз®ЎзҗҶжүҖжңү group зүҲжң¬е®ўжҲ·з«ҜпјҢж”ҜжҢҒ Discovery е’Ң RuntimeV1alpha1 |\n| Typed Client | REST е°ҒиЈ…пјҢжҸҗдҫӣ CRUD + Watch + Patch ж“ҚдҪң |\n| Informer | зј“еӯҳ + жҺ§еҲ¶еҷЁжЁЎејҸпјҢиҮӘеҠЁеҗҢжӯҘ Kubernetes иө„жәҗ |\n| Lister | еҸӘиҜ»зј“еӯҳжҹҘиҜўпјҢж”ҜжҢҒ namespace зә§еҲ«иҝҮж»Ө |\n| Scheme | зұ»еһӢеәҸеҲ—еҢ–е’ҢеҸҚеәҸеҲ—еҢ–жіЁеҶҢ |\n| Fake Client | жөӢиҜ•з”ЁеҶ…еӯҳе®һзҺ° |\n\n---\n\n## API Design\n\n### Clientset Interface\n\n```go\ntype Interface interface {\n    Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n    RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n}\n```\n\n**Constructors:**\n- `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\n- `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\n- `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\n- `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\n\n### Typed Client: RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n\n```go\ntype RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n    RESTClient() rest.Interface\n    AgentRuntimesGetter\n    CodeInterpretersGetter\n}\n```\n\n### AgentRuntimeInterface\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimeExpansion\n}\n```\n\nREST Resource: `agentruntimes`\n\n### CodeInterpreterInterface\n\nдёҺ AgentRuntimeInterface зӣёеҗҢз»“жһ„пјҢзұ»еһӢдёә `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList`пјҢREST Resource: `codeinterpreters`\n\n### Informer Factory\n\n```go\ntype SharedInformerFactory interface {\n    internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory\n    Start(stopCh <-chan struct{})\n    Shutdown()\n    WaitForCacheSync(stopCh <-chan struct{}) map[reflect.Type]bool\n    ForResource(resource schema.GroupVersionResource) (GenericInformer, error)\n    InformerFor(obj runtime.Object, newFunc internalinterfaces.NewInformerFunc) cache.SharedIndexInformer\n    Runtime() externalversionsruntime.Interface\n}\n```\n\n**Options:**\n- `NewSharedInformerFactory(client, defaultResync time.Duration)`\n- `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(client, defaultResync, options ...SharedInformerOption)`\n- Options: `WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`\n\n### Lister\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n    List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n    AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface {\n    List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Get(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Code Generation\n\n### Generation Tool\n\nдҪҝз”Ё `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1\n\n### Generation Commands\n\n```bash\nmake gen-client\n# жҲ–\nhack/update-codegen.sh\n```\n\n### Generation Flags\n\n- `--with-watch`: ж”ҜжҢҒ Watch жңәеҲ¶\n- Output package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n\n### Source Reference\n\nAPI зұ»еһӢе®ҡд№үжәҗ: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/` (еҢ…еҗ« runtime/v1alpha1 зұ»еһӢе®ҡд№ү)\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Client Errors\n\n- REST и°ғз”Ёиҝ”еӣһ `*meta.StatusError` ж—¶и§Јжһҗдёә `errors.NewStatusError`\n- зҪ‘з»ңй”ҷиҜҜгҖҒи¶…ж—¶зӣҙжҺҘдј йҖ’ Go error\n\n### Informer Errors\n\n- `WaitForCacheSync` иҝ”еӣһеҗ„ resource зҡ„еҗҢжӯҘзҠ¶жҖҒ\n- еҗҢжӯҘеӨұиҙҘдёҚеҪұе“Қе…¶д»–иө„жәҗпјҢз»§з»ӯйҮҚиҜ•\n\n### Retry Strategy\n\n- дҪҝз”Ё client-go еҶ…зҪ® retry жңәеҲ¶ (й»ҳи®ӨжҢҮж•°йҖҖйҒҝ)\n- еҸҜйҖҡиҝҮ `NewForConfigAndClient` жіЁе…ҘиҮӘе®ҡд№ү RoundTripper\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n- **Fake Client**: дҪҝз”Ё `clientset/versioned/fake/` дёӯзҡ„ fake е®һзҺ°\n  - `NewSimpleClientset()` вҖ” ж—  watch зј“еӯҳзҡ„з®ҖеҚ•е®һзҺ°\n  - `NewClientset()` вҖ” е®Ңж•ҙе®һзҺ°\n\n- **Lister Tests**: жөӢиҜ•зј“еӯҳжҹҘиҜўгҖҒnamespace иҝҮж»ӨгҖҒselector еҢ№й…Қ\n\n- **Informer Tests**: жөӢиҜ•дәӢд»¶еӨ„зҗҶгҖҒзј“еӯҳеҗҢжӯҘ\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n- еҗҜеҠЁжң¬ең° Kubernetes (kind/minikube)\n- жөӢиҜ• CRUD ж“ҚдҪңдёҺзңҹе®һ API server дәӨдә’\n\n### Fake Client Usage Example\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned/fake\"\n)\n\nclientset := fake.NewSimpleClientset()\n```\n\n---\n\n## Security Considerations\n\n### Authentication\n\n- ж”ҜжҢҒ kubeconfig дёӯзҡ„жүҖжңүи®ӨиҜҒж–№ејҸ (Bearer TokenгҖҒCertificateгҖҒOIDC)\n- йҖҡиҝҮ `rest.Config` жіЁе…ҘиҮӘе®ҡд№үеҮӯиҜҒ\n\n### Authorization\n\n- йҒөеҫӘ Kubernetes RBACпјҢclient з«ҜдёҚеҒҡйўқеӨ–жҺҲжқғжЈҖжҹҘ\n\n### Rate Limiting\n\n- еҸҜйҖҡиҝҮиҮӘе®ҡд№ү `http.Client` жіЁе…ҘйҷҗжөҒдёӯй—ҙд»¶\n\n---\n\n## Performance Optimization\n\n### Informer Cache\n\n- й»ҳи®Ө in-memory зј“еӯҳпјҢж”ҜжҢҒ CustomResyncConfig и°ғдјҳ\n- дҪҝз”Ё `WithNamespace` йҷҗеҲ¶зј“еӯҳиҢғеӣҙ\n\n### Lister Index\n\n- дҪҝз”Ё `cache.Indexer` ж”ҜжҢҒиҮӘе®ҡд№үзҙўеј•\n- й»ҳи®ӨжҢү namespace зҙўеј•\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version |\n|---------|---------|\n| k8s.io/client-go | v0.34.1 |\n| k8s.io/api | v0.34.1 |\n| k8s.io/apimachinery | v0.34.1 |\n| k8s.io/code-generator | v0.34.1 |\n\n(End of file)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/design.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/design.md","time":{"start":1775877728440,"end":1775877728464}}}}
